681
00:42:46,969 --> 00:42:48,289
<font color=#FFFF00>Pare, por favor!</font>

682
00:42:52,791 --> 00:42:54,370
<font color=#FFFF00>PAI: CHEGANDO EM 3 MINUTOS.</font>

683
00:43:41,440 --> 00:43:44,451
<font color=#FFFF00>Se tiver a chance,
