684
00:43:44,452 --> 00:43:45,752
<font color=#FFFF00>MOLHO PICANTE</font>

685
00:44:15,641 --> 00:44:17,433
<font color=#FFFF00>MADAME</font>

686
00:44:17,434 --> 00:44:20,219
<font color=#FFFF00>SEGUNDO ANDAR
SAUNA</font>

687
00:44:30,864 --> 00:44:32,456
<font color=#FFFF00>- Sente-se.
- Certo.</font>

688
00:44:34,401 --> 00:44:35,701
<font color=#FFFF00>Sr. Kim.</font>

689
00:44:35,702 --> 00:44:39,872
<font color=#FFFF00>Por favor, não conte nada disso
