708
00:46:27,773 --> 00:46:29,523
<font color=#FFFF00>Um que seja perto.</font>

709
00:46:29,524 --> 00:46:30,983
<font color=#FFFF00>Claro.</font>

710
00:46:30,984 --> 00:46:34,645
<font color=#FFFF00>- Então, o Sr. comerá fora?
