722
00:47:17,239 --> 00:47:18,823
<font color=#FFFF00>Comia demais.</font>

723
00:47:18,824 --> 00:47:21,650
<font color=#FFFF00>Ela sempre comia
por duas pessoas!</font>

724
00:47:22,410 --> 00:47:26,372
<font color=#FFFF00>Mas, considerando
