726
00:47:29,722 --> 00:47:31,636
<font color=#FFFF00>Uma nova governanta.</font>

727
00:47:31,837 --> 00:47:33,963
<font color=#FFFF00>Estamos em apuros, agora.</font>

728
00:47:33,964 --> 00:47:38,433
<font color=#FFFF00>Dentro de uma semana,
